reviewText: Absolutely terrible. An hour and 15 minutes....This review took longer for write than actually watching it. I couldn't cringe hard enough. Of course the Director gave this 5 Stars. Nothing Jersey about this, and here's an editing tip....Try to keep business signs OUT of the background.  horrible voice-overs, horrible acting...I honestly can't think of a more poorly made waste of film.
Fun, fun, fun. Clever. Well acted.
